[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 2.7"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 2.7 are now fixed in Tails 2.7.1.

We **strongly** encourage you to
[[upgrade to Tails 2.7.1|news/version_2.7.1]] as soon as possible.

Details
=======

* Tor Browser: [[!mfsa 2016-92]]
* gstreamer0.10: [[!debsa2016 3717]], [[!debsa2016 3726]]
* icu: [[!debsa2016 3725]]
* imagemagick: [[!debsa2016 3726]]
* vim: [[!debsa2016 3722]]
